<br>
Hate: No true "safe" spots exist, some are just less travelled than others. In many ways Hate is much worse for mages because the pathing there makes the big pyramid pathing in Cazic look well done. <br>
<br>
Fear: I have done over 50 fear runs now, and we have never had anyone loose a corpse. The chances of losing your corpse in Hate and Fear both come down to the same thing, do you have friends willing to help with a CR?<br>
<br>
Many mages object to going to fear simply because class armour does not drop there, I know my guild would not take a mage to Hate that did not also participate in Fear though. Lets face reality, if not for wizards, no mage would ever see Hate, and wizard armour drops in Fear. <p>Kailere Drowsbane of Veeshan -Paladin of 53 summers<BR>
